Author: -mouseytoo-
Text: I got in the habit of doing this. Especially with my roommates food cus they threw out all kinds of 'forbidden' food.    I literally ate five day old leftover mcdonalds straight out of the trash. Yes it was mouldy. Yes I scraped it off and ate the whole thing cold because I couldn't wait for the 30 seconds it would have taken to microwave it. Yes I hate myself.
